#5th, we have the American nodes downstream of Old World nodes, specifically Panama and downstream and Brazil.

#7th, we have Eastern European nodes, including more or less everything east of the HRE. Like North Africa, these nodes are immediate upstream of Western Europe, but downstream of everything else.
